---
title: HelloHero: Chicken Schnitzel & Tomato Salad with Roast Potatoes & Smokey Capsicum Relish
description: We’re putting a pep in this chicken schnitzel’s step by adding some Nan's seasoning to the golden panko crumb. Serve up with creamy roast baby potatoes to really make this dish dance and you’ll be bounding to the dinner table in excitement.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

